{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_07_02",
  "title": "兵藤雫 2話 冷房を最大に",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間後、衣装デザイナーの事務所",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few weeks later‚ at the costume designer's office",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.8000000319
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃーん……\nこれが、コンテスト用に作った新しい衣装……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ta-da…\nThis is the new costume made for the contest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.189687039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "この衣装なら……\n釣りをしてても、一目でアイドルだって分かる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With this outfit…\neven when I'm fishing‚ people will know I'm an idol at a glance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.766667223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "これでアピールはばっちり……\nこの新衣装でオーディションを突破する……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My appeal will be perfect with this…\nI'll pass the audition in this new outfit!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3027579945,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.6000006041
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "セーラーか……海で着るにはぴったりの衣装だな\n確かに、これなら目立てそうだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A sailor uniform… It’s the perfect outfit to wear at sea.\nIt certainly seems like it’ll stand out‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6666666508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.1333339375
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、浮かない顔してる……\nこの衣装に不満があるの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ you look troubled…\nIs there something you don’t like about this outfit…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3333333175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.1333339375
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "不満というか……俺は釣りのことは詳しくないが……\nその格好で冬の海釣りって、寒くないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not that I don’t like it… I’m not familiar with fishing‚ but…\nWon’t you be cold fishing in the winter sea with those clothes?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6482752397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.9000006041
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "……！！\nそれは盲点だった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…!!\nThat was a blind spot…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.166667223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、冬の海釣りは寒さとの戦い……\nこんな薄着じゃ、凍えて釣りどころじゃない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true‚ winter sea fishing is a battle against the cold…\nI can’t even fish if I’m frozen stiff in such thin clothes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7669181414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.3333319029
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そこはもっと早く気付くべきだったな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We should have noticed that sooner…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3333319029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "どうする？　この衣装は別の機会で着ることにして\n今回は他のアピール方法を考えるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you want to do? Wear this outfit on another occasion\nand come up with another way to appeal this time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0318683189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.0999985696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "それはダメ……アピールが下手な私には\nアイドル衣装が絶対必要……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way… I absolutely need an idol costume…\nsince I’m not good at appealing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.2887675717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "この衣装じゃ寒さに耐えられないのなら……\n耐えられるように、対策すればいい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I can’t withstand the cold in this outfit…\nthen I just have to take measures so I can…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4333333175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.6333319029
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "私に考えがある……\nオーディションまでに冬の寒さを攻略してみせる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have an idea…\nI’ll conquer the winter cold before the audition!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9459321685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next morning",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5000035446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.360003547
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.360003547
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "寒さを攻略すると息巻いていたが\n雫は何をする気なんだ？　無茶しないといいが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was all fired up about conquering the cold‚\nbut what’s Shizuku planning to do? I hope she’s not doing anything reckless…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8999999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、おはようございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8333339376,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 95.8333339376
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、おはよう……\n雫？　どうして練習着なんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ good morning…\nShizuku? Why are you in your workout clothes?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7333333175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.1333339376
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "コンテストに向けて、今日から毎日ランニングする……\nこれはそのための服装……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to run every day from today for the contest…\nThis is the outfit for that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.9654876316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.3000006042
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今は真冬だぞ？\nそんな薄着で外を走ったら寒いだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the middle of winter.\nYou’ll be cold running outside in such thin clothes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.0999999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "それが狙い……この格好で外を走って寒さに慣れる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s the point… I’m adapting to the cold by running outside in these clothes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0666672709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.5000006042
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "真冬に薄着でも平気でいられれば……\nセーラーで海釣りだって出来るようになるはず……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I can be fine even in thin clothes during the middle of winter…\nthen I would be able to go sea fishing in the sailor uniform too…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.4333333175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.2333339376
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "寒さを攻略するって\n気合いで我慢するって意味だったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The way of conquering the cold you meant‚\nwas enduring it with willpower?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8999999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "気合いは大事……心頭滅却すればなんとやら……\n気合いで寒さは克服出来る……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s a quote… something like “Clearing one’s mind of all mundane thoughts”…\nSo‚ willpower is important… I can overcome the cold with that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0999999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.6000006042
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "心頭滅却は熱さを我慢する時に言う言葉だからな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That quote is used when you’re enduring the heat‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.6000006042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.5000006042
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
